title: account been hacked can't click on link
body:
error 404
The page you were looking for doesn't exist

replies.body: Sometimes that can happen when your browser cache gets a little screwy. Trying [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) and if that doesn't work try logging in to view that ticket in a private/incognito window.
